{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"alias":"bluff-crane-pixel","description":"# S3 — Gerrit project + LLM-Review label + submit requirement + submitWholeTopic\n\n## Why\nThis is the gate's integrity rule: a change is submittable ONLY when the deterministic\n`LLM-Review` vote is MAX and there are no unresolved comments. `copyCondition` avoids\nre-paying for an expensive LLM review on trivial rebases; `submitWholeTopic` lands whole\nreviewed features atomically.\n\n## What\n- Create the `rebar` project in Gerrit.\n- `LLM-Review` label in `refs/meta/config`: `function=NoBlock`; values `-1..+1`;\n  `copyCondition=changekind:TRIVIAL_REBASE OR changekind:NO_CODE_CHANGE`.\n- Submit requirement `submittableIf = label:LLM-Review=MAX AND -has:unresolved`.\n- `change.submitWholeTopic=true`.\n- Access controls: grant the auto-generated `label-LLM-Review` permission to the\n  service-user group (created in S4); humans may push for review but cannot submit\n  without the label.\n\n## Scope\nIn: project + label + submit-req + topic + the label ACL. Out: the bot account itself +\nevent/vote wiring (S4); replication (S5); GitHub lockdown (S6).\n\n## Files\n- `infra/gerrit/project.config` (refs/meta/config), `infra/gerrit/setup-project.sh`\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] A change can be pushed for review to the `rebar` project; submit is BLOCKED until\n      `LLM-Review=+1` (MAX) AND there are no unresolved comments.\n- [ ] `copyCondition` carries the `LLM-Review` vote across a trivial rebase / no-code-change\n      patchset (verified by amending with no diff change).\n- [ ] `change.submitWholeTopic=true` is set (a multi-change topic submits atomically).\n- [ ] The submit requirement is the SINGLE code-review vote in v1 (no separate human\n      Code-Review and no CI Verified vote yet — those are follow-on epic 1fa8).","id":"a88d-bc7e-728b-42b6","parent_id":"d251-05e1-eb55-43b2","priority":2,"tags":["gerrit","config"],"ticket_type":"story","title":"infra: S3 — Gerrit project + LLM-Review label + submit requirement + submitWholeTopic"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1782685473948998001,"uuid":"e91bd6e9-3bbf-4cfe-8b95-7ae2c40e8e0b"}